  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Welcome to The Bathrooms, a place you may have once visited in your dreams.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with a mysterious orb and your wits, you must navigate a shifting maze of stalls and tiles. But beware, The Custodian is watching you, and somewhere in this nightmare your beloved dog, Shibosu, whimpers...waiting to be rescued.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE NIGHTMARE</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield your supernatural orb to detect danger and find keys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hide in bathroom stalls – but don't forget to lock the door behind you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the art of stealth: crouch and carefully time your movements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep the lights on, or face the horrors that lurk in darkness</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778080/extras/dbc14b4001ed097aa55edbcc7171f5ef.poster.avif?t=1761418083\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778080/extras/dbc14b4001ed097aa55edbcc7171f5ef.webm?t=1761418083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778080/extras/dbc14b4001ed097aa55edbcc7171f5ef.mp4?t=1761418083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EMBRACE THE MADNESS</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inhale Copium to boost your speed and outrun your pursuers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the legendary clown gun and fight back – if you dare</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect coins to purchase supplies from vending machines, or gamble for a big win</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778080/extras/53311a6d113c85762809496476404288.poster.avif?t=1761418083\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778080/extras/53311a6d113c85762809496476404288.webm?t=1761418083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778080/extras/53311a6d113c85762809496476404288.mp4?t=1761418083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778080/extras/bd1b070bd9d796fb5a0c3444983cc9a3.poster.avif?t=1761418083\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778080/extras/bd1b070bd9d796fb5a0c3444983cc9a3.webm?t=1761418083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778080/extras/bd1b070bd9d796fb5a0c3444983cc9a3.mp4?t=1761418083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you focus solely on your escape, or risk everything to save your faithful companion? In The Bathrooms, every decision could be your last, and salvation is always one stall away.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > More Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unpredictable and intelligent AI </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Procedurally generated world and nonlinear gameplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find collectible treasures for achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple difficulty options</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778080/extras/bfced1cc78c76f96c70c04c259205d6a.webp?t=1761418083\" width=595 height=3 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring music from <strong>Avith Ortega</strong>, <strong>Mount Shrine</strong>, and original soundtrack from <strong>Stewart Keller</strong>.   </p>",
